    <CommentBox x="54" y="87" z="-1" w="219" h="350" align="2" bgcolor="ff8040" fgcolor="0">STT&#13;
 &#13;
GPU &amp; CPU mode available&#13;
&#13;
fastwhisper python bridge wrapper&#13;
</CommentBox>
    <CommentBox x="292" y="88" z="-1" w="339" h="349" align="2" bgcolor="ff00" fgcolor="0">Intent Model&#13;
&#13;
CPU ONLY&#13;
&#13;
Parse input text with intent model to find orders to give to a robot &#13;
The model can return the following orders from natural language :&#13;
&#13;
"stop" - "forward" - "left" -"right" - "back" - "encore"&#13;
  </CommentBox>
